author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-TSMC September sales T$64.51 bln, down 13.8 pct on year
text:
Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Co Ltd
* Says September sales T$64.51 billion (August T$67.04 billion, September 2014 T$74.85 billion)
* Says September sales down 13.8 percent on year
* Says January-September sales +18.5 percent on year to T$639.98 billion Source text for Eikon: [ID: bit.ly/1grCI2q ] Further company coverage: (Reporting by J.R. Wu)
